	   <tr><td colspan=2>For Monks this is Deffinately one of the hardest Decisions to make.<br><br>Str - Hit probability and Dmg<br>Agi - Def Proc<br>Dex - Offense Proc (includes Dual Wield and Double Attack) Determines the % you attack for 4 times each round or once each combat round<br><br>To be honest with you...You want all three as High as you can get them.&nbsp;&nbsp;Strength equipment for a monk is very limited.  Most of the good one such as Hero's Braces come with a high weight penalty which you don't want.<br><br>I have 2 suggestions either balance all 3 +7 Str, +6 Agi, +7 Dex...Or put it all in str because of the lack of enhancing equipment out there.<br><br>I would deffinately consider being an iskar monk over a human one based upon starting skill points.  These far outweigh any faction problems you will have later.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
